<text top="2485" left="155" width="917" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t79" reading_order_no="44" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">This  is  just  as  well,  because  the  databases  of  tags</text>
<text top="2539" left="106" width="967" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t80" reading_order_no="45" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">and  their  bearers  maintained  by  various  governments</text>
<text top="2590" left="106" width="967" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t81" reading_order_no="46" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">don’t  stop  with  money.  In  the  name  of  homeland</text>
<text top="2641" left="106" width="967" height="63" font="font2" id="p1_t82" reading_order_no="47" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">security,  new  U.S.  passports  will  contain  standard</text>
<text top="2695" left="106" width="967" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t83" reading_order_no="48" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">passport  data  in  an  embedded  tag  that  can  trigger  the</text>
