<text top="2955" left="107" width="963" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t88" reading_order_no="53" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">increasing  control  of  the  transnational  flow  of  people.</text>
<text top="3006" left="107" width="965" height="63" font="font2" id="p1_t89" reading_order_no="54" segment_no="4" tag_type="text">By  extension,  immigration  officials  will  be  able  to</text>
