<text top="1654" left="1404" width="695" height="55" font="font0" id="p1_t95" reading_order_no="94" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">stalking,  and  commercial  data  collec-</text>
<text top="1701" left="1405" width="701" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t96" reading_order_no="95" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">tion  [11],  perhaps  with  the  intent  of</text>
