<text top="1811" left="1128" width="971" height="55" font="font0" id="p1_t98" reading_order_no="97" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">tions  of  RFID-tagged  goods  and  cash.  Indeed,  retail-</text>
<text top="1856" left="1127" width="973" height="65" font="font1" id="p1_t99" reading_order_no="98" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">ers  are  concerned  that  thieves  equipped  with  mobile</text>
<text top="1910" left="1126" width="973" height="62" font="font3" id="p1_t100" reading_order_no="99" segment_no="7" tag_type="text">REID  devices  will  create  new  and  sophisticated  ways</text>
